1. *Di* se za njega pričalo u selu. (People were talking about him in the village.)
2. *Di* se išlo? (Where did you go?)
3. *Di* si ti tu? (What are you doing here?)
4. *Di* si bila? (Where were you?)
5. *Di* ćeš ići? (Where are you going?)
6. *Di* ti je kaput? (Where is your coat?)
7. *Di* su ti čizme? (Where are your boots?)
8. On zna *di* da ide. (He knows where to go.)
9. Ona zna *di* da stane. (She knows where to stand.)
10. On zna *di* da se okrene. (He knows where to turn.)